Day 31 of #circuitbreaker: Anyone missing @mcdsg? Ian ask me “Mummy when is Mc Donald’s gonna be reopen? I miss their breakfast set, remember we always order on Sunday mornings?”⁣
⁣
Walking pass all the closed McDonald’s is a strange feeling. I am still waiting...hopefully soon 😵⁣
